/*!
@page geminidataanalytics-override-endpoint How to Override the Default Endpoint

In some cases, you may need to override the default endpoint used by the client
library. Use the
[EndpointOption](@ref google::cloud::EndpointOption) when initializing the
client library to change this default.

<!-- inject-endpoint-snippet-start -->
For example, this will override the default endpoint for `geminidataanalytics_v1::DataAgentServiceClient`:

@snippet data_agent_client_samples.cc set-client-endpoint

Follow these links to find examples for other \c *Client classes:

- [\c geminidataanalytics_v1::DataAgentServiceClient](@ref geminidataanalytics_v1::DataAgentServiceClient-endpoint-snippet)
- [\c geminidataanalytics_v1::DataChatServiceClient](@ref geminidataanalytics_v1::DataChatServiceClient-endpoint-snippet)

<!-- inject-endpoint-snippet-end -->

*/

